Introduction
Raif Şelle built the Kids songs app as a Free app. This SERVICE is provided by Raif Şelle at no cost and is intended for use as is.
We understand how important privacy is to you and your family, which is why we are committed to creating a safe and secure environment that family members of all ages can enjoy. As a developer studio, our only goal is to serve a good and benefits app to users, and we don't collect any information from the users. So, if you have any question or idea, it is up to you to give us your opinion, or just use the app as you need.

Children’s Privacy
We are committed to protecting the privacy needs of children and we encourage parents and guardians to take an active role in their children’s online activities and interests. Our applications are fully COPPA compliant, as we said, our application is not collecting any information from users.

What information does the Application obtain and how is it used ?
-User Provided Information
The Application obtains the information you provide when you download the application, or when you buy the NoAds package, that is the only information we get.

-Automatically Collected Information
No automatically information collecting in our app, even third party ads we display, it is not depending on location, and we don't let them collect any information about locations of users, we never share any information with them too !

Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here and informing you via the app.

Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at Rhhs0940@gmail.com.

